OL,3,CThames Water faces wait to discover if
OL,4,Crestructure approval will be overturned
OL,6,FThames Water must wait to discover
OL,7,Fwhether the approval of a plan to
OL,8,Frestructure the struggling utility
OL,9,Fwill be overturned at the Court of
OL,10,FAppeal.
OL,12,FIn February, a High Court judge
OL,13,Fsanctioned a plan proposed by Thames
OL,14,FWater Utilities Holdings Limited
OL,15,F(TWUH), the parent company of Thames
OL,16,FWater Group, allowing the utility to
OL,17,Fstay afloat just weeks before it was
OL,18,Fdue to run out of money.
