OL,3,CThames Water faces wait to discover if
OL,4,Crestructure approval will be overturned
OL,6,FAt the end of the hearing on Thursday,
OL,7,FSir Julian Flaux, sitting with Sir
OL,8,FNicholas Patten and Lord Justice
OL,9,FZacaroli, said that they would hand
OL,10,Fdown their judgment in writing at a
OL,11,Flater date.
OL,13,FHe added: "We will do the best we can
OL,14,Fto give you an answer to whether the
OL,15,Fappeal is allowed or dismissed,
OL,16,Fhopefully during the course of next
OL,17,Fweek."
