OL,3,CThames Water faces wait to discover if
OL,4,Crestructure approval will be overturned
OL,6,FAndrew Thornton KC, for TWL,
OL,7,Fpreviously told the court in written
OL,8,Fsubmissions that the approved plan was
OL,9,F"designed by senior lenders for the
OL,10,Fbenefit of senior lenders".
OL,12,FHe said that the terms of the plan
OL,13,Fwere "mispriced and inappropriate".
OL,15,FHe continued that the judge, Mr
OL,16,FJustice Leech, "failed to apply the
OL,17,Fcorrect principles" when making his
OL,18,Fdecision to approve the scheme, and
OL,19,Ftherefore "wrongly exercised his
OL,20,Fdiscretion to sanction the plan".
