OL,3,CThames Water faces wait to discover if
OL,4,Crestructure approval will be overturned
OL,6,FTWUH and its Class A creditors are
OL,7,Fopposing the appeal, with Tom Smith
OL,8,FKC, for TWUH, stating in written
OL,9,Fsubmissions that the Court of Appeal
OL,10,Fshould not interfere with the decision
OL,11,F"unless compelled to do so".
OL,13,FBarristers for Mr Maynard, the MP for
OL,14,FWitney in Oxfordshire, previously told
OL,15,Fthe High Court that allowing the
OL,16,Fcompany to enter SAR was a "better and
OL,17,Ffairer course" which served "the
OL,18,Fpublic interest and customers'
OL,19,Finterests".
