OL,3,CThames Water faces wait to discover if
OL,4,Crestructure approval will be overturned
OL,6,FWilliam Day, for the MP, told the
OL,7,Fcourt in written submissions: "The
OL,8,Fplan should be rejected on the basis
OL,9,Fthat its terms and cost are much worse
OL,10,Ffor the Thames Water Group, in
OL,11,Fparticular, TWUL, than rescue by
OL,12,Fspecial administration."
OL,14,FThames Water serves about 16 million
OL,15,Fcustomers ` about 25% of the UK's
OL,16,Fpopulation ` and owns more than 20,000
OL,17,Fmiles of water mains and more than
OL,18,F68,000 miles of sewers across London,
OL,19,Fthe Thames Valley and the Home
OL,20,FCounties.
